    "long_instructions": "1. **Prompt and Refine**  \r\n   Ask AI to recreate your chosen feature from Level 1. If it’s off, ask for a fix.\r\n   &nbsp\r\n   \r\n   - _Example Initial Prompt_: “Create a nav bar with a logo left and 3 links right.”\r\n   - _Example Revision Prompt_: “Add more spacing between the links.”\r\n\r\n2. **Save Version 1 (v1)**  \r\n   When it looks right, open Version History and describe your changes with a short message. For example, *“v1 – working nav bar.”* Then click Save version.\r\n   - :::details [**Show Me How**]\r\n   ![](https://images.code.org/f7f0c57a1ef627b02e94c09014cfe128-image-1760477045364.gif)\r\n   :::\r\n\r\n:::details [**(Optional) Break It On Purpose**]\r\n   Try a risky prompt (e.g., “Rebuild layout with CSS Grid everywhere”).  \r\n   Observe what breaks, then **Revert** to your saved v1.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
